Proxomo,is,a,cloud,infrastructure,solution,specifically,designed,with,mobile,developers,in,mind,The,tool,kit,is,for,social,location,aware,applications,The,Proxomo,services,help,developers,realize,results,faster,and,cheaper,by,allowing,them,to,focus,on,the,mobile,app,or,website,freeing,them,from,worrying,about,developing,connections,to,external,services,and,rolling,a,scalable,server,infrastructure,for,hosting,Proxomo,s,API,allows,third,party,developers,to,leverage,this,platform,in,any,given,social,context,Proxomo,helps,developers,store,application,data,interact,with,events,invitations,access,friend,graph,information,currently,from,Facebook,geocode,users,via,IP,or,address,store,and,access,location,data,create,SMS,notifications,and,storing,user,preferences,and,data,The,API,uses,RESTful,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON